{"tid":254324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁振英：會盡全力保護個人權益和聲譽","createTime":"2017-05-23T06:20:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-26T04:23:57.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"399aa39b9375903b6e8931044df16c423767cc9f","tid":254324,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T06:20:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/23/142004_687f048285624920f9963c8b43092996.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F23%2F142004_687f048285624920f9963c8b43092996.jpg&h=7e4f0b32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】行政長官梁振英批評，28名議員提出彈劾議案是濫用機制，強調會盡全力保護個人權益和聲譽，他沒回應會否出席UGL專責委員會的聆訊。<br />\n<br />\n梁振英出席行政會議前再回應UGL事件，批評28名立法會議員聯署提出彈劾議案<br />\n<br />\n他主動提到，港大法律學者張達明在社交網站對他提出的九點質疑，認為對方不了解事件的來龍去脈。<br />\n<br />\n被問到會否出席UGL專責委員會的聆訊，詳細解釋各項質疑，他無回應，只表示自己已全面回應UGL事件，並再要求梁繼昌退出委員會。<br />\n<br />\n他重申，英國與澳洲的稅局和執法機關均沒向他提出調查或起訴，認為立法會對他的調查不公道。"},{"pid":"28f5b8303369aba3ff21fc320e2d0b7671276192","tid":254324,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T06:20:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=222147\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D222147&d=qBthqP3FTW7irafgb228CJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=10544c6b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D222147&h=fd0c4821\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=222147</a>"},{"pid":"4d4050018778f961d8d0aa6d2cdc0d8b2f2d3320","tid":254324,"uid":68491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T06:21:27.000Z","msg":"張相正"},{"pid":"37c88820c9aa598ae2af27d086b306fe8e80ff1a","tid":254324,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T06:21:37.000Z","msg":"暴走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal